2 unit Gala Apple
6 unit Flour Tortillas
86 g Cream Cheese
4 tbsp Blueberry Jam
170 g Red Grapes
132 g Mini Cucumber

Before starting, wash and dry all produce.

Halve grapes. Cut cucumbers in half lengthwise, then into spears. Core, then cut apples into 1/2-inch wedges.

Spread cream cheese over each tortilla, then spoon blueberry jam over top.

Top tortillas with grapes. Tightly roll up each tortilla over grapes and filling. Serve with cucumbers spears and apple slices on the side.